data.description: POOL HOME! Welcome to this stunning home featuring four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and more than 2,200 square feet of living space. The perfect home for entertaining with a great layout and flow. Step into your own backyard oasis where you'll find a heated pool, perfect for year-round enjoyment. Enjoy the covered patio that provides a lovely space for outdoor gatherings and entertainment. The lush, vibrant turf offers a low-maintenance solution and a picture-perfect lawn year-round. Additionally, a convenient shed stands ready to accommodate your storage needs. Inside, the house has been completely upgraded, showcasing modern and stylish finishes throughout. The oversized kitchen is a standout with its spacious layout, large island, and ample storage. The large family room is perfect for gatherings, featuring large windows filling the room with plenty of natural light and a cozy fireplace. All of the upstairs bedrooms are generously sized and the spacious master bedroom features a convenient walk-in closet. The roof was replaced just a couple of years ago, ensuring durability and longevity. The hot water tank was recently replaced in 2020, and the HVAC system is not very old.  Pool liner was recently replaced and the pump is soon to be as well. Situated on a corner lot, the home offers a great location off NW Expressway with easy access to a wide range of shopping and dining options, making it a highly convenient and desirable place to call home. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your forever home!
